<!-- Description -->
<div style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">
<h2 style="color: #0d5e6d;">Welcome to East Coast Holiday Hotel</h2>
<p>Nestled in the picturesque town of Charikot in Nepal's Dolakha district, East Coast Holiday Hotel offers the perfect blend of comfort, affordability, and authentic Nepalese hospitality. Our family-run establishment provides a cozy retreat for travelers exploring the stunning Himalayan foothills and surrounding valleys.</p>
<p>With panoramic mountain views, clean comfortable rooms, and a friendly staff that treats you like family, East Coast Holiday Hotel is the ideal base for your adventures in the region. Whether you're trekking to nearby destinations, visiting local temples, or simply enjoying the peaceful ambiance of Charikot, our hotel provides a welcoming home away from home.</p>
<p>Our commitment to personalized service and attention to detail ensures that every guest experiences the true essence of Nepalese hospitality during their stay with us.</p>
</div>
